# Hand Sign Language Recognition for Mute Support via Webcam

## Overview
Real-time hand sign language recognition system using deep learning to support communication for mute individuals.

## Features
- Real-time hand gesture detection using CNN
- Live webcam integration
- Text and speech output
- User-friendly interface

## Technologies
- Python
- TensorFlow/Keras
- OpenCV
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn

## Installation
```bash
pip install tensorflow keras opencv-python numpy scikit-learn
```

## Usage
```bash
python train.py      # Train the model
python test.py       # Test the model
```

## Project Structure
```
├── train.py          # Model training script
├── test.py           # Model testing script
├── data/             # Dataset directory
└── models/           # Trained models
```

